 对任意“紧支 (compact supported) 光滑函数” 
\begin_inset Formula $\phi(x,t)$
\end_inset

 都满足
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\int_{t_{0}}^{+\infty}\int_{-\infty}^{+\infty}\left(\pdv{\phi}{t}U+\pdv{\phi}{x}F\right)\dd{x}\dd{t}+\int_{-\infty}^{+\infty}\phi\mathopen{}\left(x_{0},t_{0}\right)U_{0}(x_{0})\dd{x_{0}}=0
\]

\end_inset

则称 
\begin_inset Formula $U(x,t)$
\end_inset

 为该初值问题的一个“弱解 (weak solution)”
